重傷的林姓司機家屬4日晚透過縱橫聯合法律事務所所長周武榮律師公開聲明，記者會說法不實，並指友寄和Makiyo等以此脫責混淆視聽，犯罪後態度實屬惡劣<ref>{{cite news |title=受傷司機家屬駁斥Makiyo說詞不實 |url=http://udn.com/NEWS/BREAKINGNEWS/BREAKINGNEWS2/6879902.shtml |publisher=聯合報 |date=2012-02-04 |accessdate=2012-02-07 |archive-date=2012-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206204403/http://udn.com/NEWS/BREAKINGNEWS/BREAKINGNEWS2/6879902.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。臺北市議員[[賴素如|賴素如]]7日下午陪同司機服務的車行經理召開記者會時，也透露林姓司機的妻子一度被友寄隆輝帶黑道恐嚇，要求盡快和解，因此嚇到不敢開記者會<ref>{{cite news|title=大事想化小？！ 傳Makiyo日友人帶黑道恐嚇？|url=http://www.nownews.com/2012/02/07/91-2782881.htm|publisher=NOWnews|date=2012-02-07|accessdate=2012-02-07|archive-date=2012-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120507004042/http://www.nownews.com/2012/02/07/91-2782881.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====Makiyo偕母赴醫院探視====
2月5日，友寄兩度赴醫院探視遭拒<ref>{{cite news |title=5萬網友 嗆Makiyo退演藝圈 |url=http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/34003663/IssueID/20120206 |publisher=蘋果日報 |date=2012-02-06 |access-date=2012-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208012257/http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/34003663/IssueID/20120206 |archive-date=2012-02-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，Makiyo則和母親在下午3時許，前往探視受傷司機。在林姓司機妻子的面前，Makiyo當場道歉，Makiyo母女否認說過司機襲胸的言論，為此在媒體面前向家屬辯駁<ref>{{cite news |title=Makiyo到醫院痛哭道歉　司機妻：睜眼說瞎話 |url=http://www.nownews.com/2012/02/05/340-2782145.htm |publisher=NOWnews |date=2012-02-05 |accessdate=2012-02-09 |archive-date=2012-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427145212/http://www.nownews.com/2012/02/05/340-2782145.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=日籍友毆傷運將 Makiyo、Ma媽媽醫院道歉 |url=http://video.chinatimes.com/video-cate-cnt.aspx?cid=5&nid=72787 |publisher=中天新聞 |date=2012-02-05 |accessdate=2012-02-09 |archive-date=2012-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120511190807/http://video.chinatimes.com/video-cate-cnt.aspx?cid=5&nid=72787 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Makiyo母親對家屬表示2月4日的聲明稿並不是她們發的，但她們只能認錯，Makiyo則稱自己酒醉，事情已不太清楚<ref>{{cite news |title=聲淚俱下！Makiyo痛哭 向家屬道歉 |url=http://udn.com/NEWS/SOCIETY/SOC8/6880510.shtml |publisher=聯合新聞網 |date=2012-02-05 |accessdate=2012-02-09 |archive-date=2012-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208123937/http://udn.com/NEWS/SOCIETY/SOC8/6880510.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Makiyo不認發聲明稿　網友嗆：難道是鬼發的！ |url=http://m.ettoday.net/news/20120205/22948.htm |publisher=ETtoday |date=2012-02-05 |accessdate=2012-02-09 |archive-date=2012-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120207134729/http://m.ettoday.net/news/20120205/22948.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====丫子、湘瑩身份曝光====
2月6日，經影片比對後，發現案發當晚和友寄、Makiyo同行的另兩名女性為[[丫子|丫子]]與[[湘瑩|湘瑩]]2名女藝人。檢方當晚發出傳票，傳喚Makiyo、丫子、湘瑩等3人<ref>{{cite news |title=Makiyo 3女星昨漏夜被偵訊 揪出ㄚ子湘瑩共犯 |url=http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/34005415/IssueID/20120207 |publisher=蘋果日報 |date=2012-02-07 |access-date=2012-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209014917/http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/34005415/IssueID/20120207 |archive-date=2012-02-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。承辦檢察官以證人身份約談Makiyo，隨後將她改列被告，訊後依毀棄損壞、重傷害等罪嫌，諭令新台幣3萬元交保，並限制出境；丫子、湘瑩訊後則遭請回。訊後3人面對大批媒體，數度鞠躬致歉<ref name="#4">{{cite news |title=Makiyo從證人改列被告　3萬元交保 |url=http://tw.nextmedia.com/realtimenews/article/new/20120207/109051/ |publisher=蘋果日報 |date=2012-02-07 |access-date=2012-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209084420/http://tw.nextmedia.com/realtimenews/article/new/20120207/109051 |archive-date=2012-02-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

湘瑩是事發後唯一一個不斷打電話、傳簡訊關心司機的人。司機願意原諒湘瑩。司機太太表示，自先生從轉出加護病房，就有說坐在前座的女孩子很無辜，湘瑩聽到此話激動落淚<ref>{{cite news |title=湘瑩探視被毆運將　林姓司機：願意原諒妳 |url=http://tw.nextmedia.com/realtimenews/article/entertainment/20120313/114237 |publisher=蘋果日報 |date=2012-03-13 |access-date=2012-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316013416/http://tw.nextmedia.com/realtimenews/article/entertainment/20120313/114237 |archive-date=2012-03-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

====Makiyo涉案畫面公布====
2月8日，一名江姓司機提供的影片經媒體播出，片長約50秒的影片顯示Makiyo在林姓司機倒地後起腳補踹，不顧友寄勸阻而拚命攻擊，Makiyo還換邊補踹一腳，司機在50秒內共被踹了15腳<ref>{{cite news |title=東森獨家! Makiyo狠踹倒地運將 |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ut87QSndGaA |publisher=東森新聞 |date=2012-02-08 |accessdate=2012-02-08 |archive-date=2014-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140430070712/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ut87QSndGaA |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Makiyo 2度狠踹運將 |url=http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/34012770/IssueID/20120209 |publisher=蘋果日報 |date=2012-02-09 |access-date=2012-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209033006/http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/34012770/IssueID/20120209 |archive-date=2012-02-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[臺灣臺北地方法院檢察署|台北地檢署]]9日下午赴醫院就訊林姓司機，並以被告身份傳喚Makiyo與友寄<ref>{{cite news |title=檢下午密訊被害司機 了解遭毆經過 |url=http://udn.com/NEWS/SOCIETY/SOC8/6890408.shtml |publisher=中央通訊社 |date=2012-02-09}}</ref>。訊後檢方諭令Makiyo、友寄各加保新台幣5萬元，至於以證人身分傳喚的丫子、湘瑩兩人，訊後改列[[偽證罪|偽證罪]]被告。湘瑩因改口看到Makiyo有踢人的動作，坦承偽證，檢方諭令3萬元交保；丫子則否認看到Makiyo踢人，諭令5萬元交保<ref name="#5">{{cite news |title=Makiyo友寄 各加保5萬 |url=http://www2.cna.com.tw/News/aSOC/201202090332.aspx |publisher=中央通訊社 |date=2012-02-09 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=影帶現聲 Makiyo涉教唆施暴 |url=http://showbiz.chinatimes.com/showbiz/110511/112012021000001.html |publisher=中國時報 |date=2012-02-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212004013/http://showbiz.chinatimes.com/showbiz/110511/112012021000001.html |archivedate=2012-02-12 }}</ref>。

2月10日，臺北地檢署偵查終結，於晚間召開記者會說明，檢方認定友寄手段凶殘，Makiyo犯後說詞反覆、態度惡劣，將兩人以重傷害罪起訴，友寄具體求刑6年，Makiyo具體求刑4年。湘瑩和丫子涉及偽証罪部分，另行偵結<ref name="聯合0211">{{cite news |title=重傷害起訴 Makiyo求刑4年 友寄6年 |url=http://udn.com/NEWS/SOCIETY/SOC8/6892276.shtml |publisher=聯合新聞網 |date=2012-02-11 |accessdate=2012-02-10 |archive-date=2012-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213012924/http://udn.com/NEWS/SOCIETY/SOC8/6892276.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

