Makiyo所代言的產品與投資的忍者餐廳也被網友列入抵制的對象，數間代言商家都表示不會再聘請Makiyo<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nownews.com/2012/02/05/138-2782084.htm |title=Makiyo友人打傷運將又卸責　網友：抵制Makiyo代言產品 |access-date=2012-02-07 |archive-date=2012-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120513050553/http://www.nownews.com/2012/02/05/138-2782084.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20120207/5764069.html |title=Makiyo道歉無效遭網友抵制錯失商家代言 |access-date=2012-02-07 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117230706/http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20120207/5764069.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Makiyo因為被起訴，所以3年內將無法取得工作證進入臺灣工作<ref>[http://tw.news.yahoo.com/makiyo%E9%86%89%E6%83%B9%E7%A6%8D-ma%E8%A2%AB%E8%A8%B4%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%AD%89%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%9D-3%E5%B9%B4%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-105923998.html Makiyo醉惹禍／Ma被訴工作證不保　3年無法入台工作] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214031602/http://tw.news.yahoo.com/makiyo%E9%86%89%E6%83%B9%E7%A6%8D-ma%E8%A2%AB%E8%A8%B4%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%AD%89%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%9D-3%E5%B9%B4%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-105923998.html |date=2012-02-14 }}</ref>。勞委會職訓局外勞管理組已在2月16日發文廢止她的在台工作證<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20120305/29496.htm |title=Makiyo在台工作證廢止　3年內不能打工 |access-date=2012-03-05 |archive-date=2012-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718071939/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20120305/29496.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

